Staff Reporter JOHANNESBURG- A video of a man who allegedly raped a seven-year-old girl at the Dros restaurant in Silverton‚ Pretoria‚ has emerged. The video shows, a naked man with blood covering most of his face, in the men’s toilet and patrons are lashing out at him as seen on the video. The suspect, who by law, cannot be identified until his plea is heard, is expected to appear at the Pretoria Regional Court on October 2, Dros restaurant on Wednesday released a statement saying: “We have been in contact with the parents of the child to convey our sympathy and offered our assistance in any form that would (or could) reasonably be required in a matter of this nature,” Reports of the alleged rape first surfaced on Facebook on Saturday, Netwerk24 reported. SENSITIVE VIDEO: SEE THE VIDEO BELOW